Class Contract

java.lang.Object
hr.java.restaurant.model.Contract
public class Contract extends Object
Represents an employment contract for a worker, with details such as salary, contract dates, and contract type.

      public Contract(BigDecimal salary, LocalDate startDate, LocalDate endDate, Contract.ContractType contractType)
      Constructs a new Contract object with the specified salary, start date, end date, and contract type.
      Parameters:
      salary - The salary for the employee.
      startDate - The start date of the contract.
      endDate - The end date of the contract.
      contractType - The type of the contract (either Contract.ContractType.FULL_TIME or Contract.ContractType.PART_TIME).
